Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.74,1:09:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00484848\bord0\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\b1\frx0\fs40\fry356\frz325\pos(324,448.555)}為救援捷克軍…
